title: Tech's season ends with loss to UMD in NCAA Tournament - michigantechhuskies.com
content: Tech's season ends with loss to UMD in NCAA Tournament  michigantechhuskies.com
description: The Michigan Tech hockey season came to an end in the NCAA West Region Semifinal as the No. 14-ranked Huskies fell 3-0 to No. 6 Minnesota Duluth.
